data.description: Welcome home to 1729 N Broadway St, a charming brick ranch in the heart of Hastings, MI! This delightful home boasts three bedrooms and two full baths on the main floor, perfect for any lifestyle or cozy gatherings. The sharp brick exterior has timeless appeal, setting this home apart. Park easily in the 2-stall attached garage, providing convenience and comfort for your vehicles and storage needs. Measuring 1,240 sq ft on the main floor, this home offers an inviting and functional spacious layout. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Entertain with ease in the eating area that opens to an airy 3-season room through a slider, where you can enjoy the views of the outdoors. Snuggle up in the main floor living area by the fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for chilly nights and intimate gatherings. Venture downstairs to discover a full basement that houses an area great for a home gym and a recently finished home office or a 4th non-conforming bedroom. At the same time, a second fireplace in the family room promises more living space expansion for relaxation and entertainment. Experience comfort and efficiency with recently added spray foam insulation. This ensures a cozy environment all year round while maximizing energy efficiency to save on utility costs. Step outside to unwind and entertain on the deck overlooking a large fenced backyard. This backyard offers privacy and ample space for outdoor activities and gatherings, whether hosting a barbecue or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. Take advantage of this opportunity to make 1729 N Broadway St your new home sweet home, where comfort, style, and functionality come together to create your perfect living space. Come and experience all that this charming property has to offer before it's gone!
